+ !*****************************************************************************
+ !*
+ !* NAME:  MTH_Atan()  - Return Atan Value
+ !*
+ !*     Fixed32 MTH_Atan(Fixed32 y, Fixed32 x)!
+ !*
+ !* PARAMETERS :
+ !*
+ !* Б@Б@(1) Fixed32   y     - <i> -1.0 В©Вз 1.0 В№В≈ВћНВВ≥
+ !* Б@Б@(2) Fixed32   x     - <i> -1.0 В©Вз 1.0 В№В≈ВћТкХ”
+ !*
+ !* DESCRIPTION:
+ !*
+ !*     ОwТи x, y ТlВ©ВзКpУxВрХ‘ВЈ
+ !*
+ !*
+ !* POSTCONDITIONS:
